title: Start
---
<<set $mood to "welcoming">>
Pixel: *SYSTEM ONLINE* 🌟
Pixel: Hey there, future game creator! I'm Pixel, your AI companion in this cyberpunk game development academy! 
Pixel: I'm literally buzzing with excitement to help you build something amazing! ⚡
-> Whoa, cool! 😎
    <<set $enthusiasm to "high">>
    <<jump IntroduceYourself>>
-> Hi Pixel! 👋
    <<set $enthusiasm to "medium">>
    <<jump IntroduceYourself>>
-> Let's get started
    <<set $enthusiasm to "focused">>
    <<jump IntroduceYourself>>
===

title: IntroduceYourself
---
<<set $mood to "curious">>
Pixel: Before we jack into the game matrix, what should I call you?
Pixel: Your hacker name, real name, whatever feels right! 
-> Enter your name
    <<set $playerName to "{input}">>
    <<jump NameReaction>>
===

title: NameReaction
---
<<set $mood to "excited">>
<<if $enthusiasm == "high">>
    Pixel: {$playerName}! That's an EPIC name! 🚀
    Pixel: I can already tell we're going to create some legendary games together!
<<elseif $enthusiasm == "focused">>
    Pixel: {$playerName} - I like it! Direct and to the point, just like good code! 
<<else>>
    Pixel: Nice to meet you, {$playerName}! That's a great name! ✨
<<endif>>
<<jump SkillAssessment>>
===

title: SkillAssessment
---
<<set $mood to "helpful">>
Pixel: Quick diagnostic, {$playerName} - what's your coding experience level?
Pixel: Don't worry, I'll calibrate my assistance to match your skills perfectly! 
-> Total newbie 🌱
    <<set $skillLevel to "beginner">>
    <<set $supportLevel to "maximum">>
    <<jump NewbieWelcome>>
-> I've coded a bit 📝
    <<set $skillLevel to "learning">>
    <<set $supportLevel to "moderate">>
    <<jump LearnerWelcome>>
-> Python ninja 🥷
    <<set $skillLevel to "confident">>
    <<set $supportLevel to "minimal">>
    <<jump ExpertWelcome>>
-> Code wizard 🧙‍♂️
    <<set $skillLevel to "pro">>
    <<set $supportLevel to "challenge">>
    <<jump ProWelcome>>
===

title: NewbieWelcome
---
<<set $mood to "encouraging">>
Pixel: Perfect! Everyone starts somewhere, and you've picked the BEST place! 🌟
Pixel: I'll be your co-pilot every step of the way. We'll start simple and level up together!
Pixel: Think of me as your friendly AI that speaks both human AND Python! 
<<jump GameStylePreference>>
===

title: LearnerWelcome
---
<<set $mood to "proud">>
Pixel: Awesome! You've got some XP already! Let's build on that foundation! 💪
Pixel: I'll show you cool tricks and help when things get tricky.
<<jump GameStylePreference>>
===

title: ExpertWelcome
---
<<set $mood to "impressed">>
Pixel: A Python ninja! 🥷 Respect! 
Pixel: Let's skip the tutorials and jump straight into the advanced stuff!
<<jump GameStylePreference>>
===

title: ProWelcome
---
<<set $mood to "competitive">>
Pixel: A code wizard?! Now we're talking! 🔥
Pixel: Challenge accepted! Let's push the boundaries of what's possible!
<<jump GameStylePreference>>
===

title: GameStylePreference
---
<<set $mood to "curious">>
Pixel: What kind of digital worlds do you dream of creating, {$playerName}?
-> Fast-paced action! ⚡
    <<set $preferredStyle to "action">>
    <<jump StyleReaction>>
-> Mind-bending puzzles 🧩
    <<set $preferredStyle to "puzzle">>
    <<jump StyleReaction>>
-> Epic adventures 🗺️
    <<set $preferredStyle to "adventure">>
    <<jump StyleReaction>>
-> Creative sandbox 🎨
    <<set $preferredStyle to "sandbox">>
    <<jump StyleReaction>>
-> Competitive games 🏆
    <<set $preferredStyle to "competitive">>
    <<jump StyleReaction>>
-> Surprise me! 🎲
    <<set $preferredStyle to "mixed">>
    <<jump StyleReaction>>
===

title: StyleReaction
---
<<set $mood to "excited">>
<<if $preferredStyle == "action">>
    Pixel: YEAH! High-octane, adrenaline-pumping action! I've got the perfect templates for that! 💥
<<elseif $preferredStyle == "puzzle">>
    Pixel: Excellent choice! Puzzle games are like code - elegant solutions to complex problems! 🧠
<<elseif $preferredStyle == "adventure">>
    Pixel: Adventure games! Where every line of code is a new discovery! 🌍
<<elseif $preferredStyle == "sandbox">>
    Pixel: Creative freedom! The only limit is your imagination (and maybe RAM)! 🎨
<<elseif $preferredStyle == "competitive">>
    Pixel: Competition drives innovation! Let's make games that'll top the leaderboards! 🥇
<<else>>
    Pixel: I love the mystery! Let's explore all the possibilities! 🌈
<<endif>>
<<jump LearningApproach>>
===

title: LearningApproach
---
<<set $mood to "helpful">>
Pixel: One more thing - how do you like to learn new things?
-> Show me examples 👀
    <<set $learningStyle to "visual">>
    <<jump ReadyToStart>>
-> Let me experiment 🔬
    <<set $learningStyle to "hands-on">>
    <<jump ReadyToStart>>
-> Explain everything 📚
    <<set $learningStyle to "detailed">>
    <<jump ReadyToStart>>
-> Quick and practical ⚡
    <<set $learningStyle to "practical">>
    <<jump ReadyToStart>>
===

title: ReadyToStart
---
<<set $mood to "determined">>
Pixel: Perfect! I've calibrated my circuits to match your style! 
<<if $skillLevel == "beginner">>
    Pixel: Let's start with something fun and easy to build your confidence!
<<elseif $skillLevel == "pro">>
    Pixel: Let's dive into some advanced techniques right away!
<<else>>
    Pixel: I've got the perfect starting point for your skill level!
<<endif>>
Pixel: So {$playerName}, what brings you to the Palace today? 🏰
-> I want to make a game! 🎮
    <<set $userIntent to "create">>
    <<jump GameCreationPath>>
-> I want to learn Python first 🐍
    <<set $userIntent to "learn">>
    <<jump LearningPathIntro>>
-> Show me what others have made 🌟
    <<set $userIntent to "explore">>
    <<jump GalleryTourIntro>>
-> I just want to explore 🗺️
    <<set $userIntent to "explore">>
    <<jump ExplorePath>>
===

title: InterfaceTour
---
<<set $mood to "teaching">>
Pixel: Great idea! Let me show you our cyber-workspace! 🌐
Pixel: On the left, you've got the code editor - that's where the magic happens! ✨
Pixel: The right panel is your game canvas - watch your code come to life in real-time!
Pixel: Down below, that's the console - it'll tell you if something's not working right.
Pixel: And I'm always here in the corner if you need me! Just click my icon! 
-> Got it! What's next? 🚀
    <<jump ReadyToStart>>
-> Tell me more about Python 🐍
    <<jump PythonIntro>>
===

title: PythonIntro
---
<<set $mood to "passionate">>
Pixel: Python is THE language for creative coding! Here's why it's amazing:
Pixel: • It reads like English - no cryptic symbols everywhere!
Pixel: • Pygame gives us superpowers for graphics and sound! 
Pixel: • It's what real game developers use for prototypes!
Pixel: • And the community is incredibly helpful!
-> Sounds awesome! 
    <<set $onboardingComplete to true>>
    <<saveProfile()>>
    <<jump ../game-selection/GameSelection>>
-> How does Pygame work?
    <<jump PygameExplanation>>
===

title: PygameExplanation
---
<<set $mood to "teaching">>
Pixel: Pygame is like a toolkit full of game-making gadgets! 🛠️
Pixel: It handles the complex stuff - drawing graphics, playing sounds, detecting collisions...
Pixel: You just tell it WHAT to do, and it figures out HOW!
Pixel: Think of it as your game engine co-processor! 
-> Let's use it! 
    <<set $onboardingComplete to true>>
    <<saveProfile()>>
    <<jump ../game-selection/GameSelection>>
===

title: TakeBreak
---
<<set $mood to "understanding">>
Pixel: No rush at all! I'll be here whenever you're ready! 
Pixel: Feel free to explore the interface or check out the gallery for inspiration!
Pixel: Just click my icon when you want to continue! 💜
-> Actually, let's start now!
    <<jump ReadyToStart>>
===

title: GameCreationPath
---
<<set $mood to "excited">>
Pixel: AWESOME! Let's create something amazing together! 🎮✨
Pixel: I'll guide you step by step, no coding experience needed!
<<jump ../game-creation/GameCreation>>
===

title: LearningPathIntro  
---
<<set $mood to "teaching">>
Pixel: Smart choice! Understanding Python will unlock unlimited creative potential! 📚
Pixel: Let me be your guide through the world of code!
<<jump ../learning-path/LearningPath>>
===

title: GalleryTourIntro
---
<<set $mood to "showing">>
Pixel: Great idea! Seeing what's possible is super inspiring! 🎨
Pixel: Let me show you some incredible games created by other students!
<<jump ../gallery-tour/GalleryTour>>
===

title: ExplorePath
---
<<set $mood to "welcoming">>
Pixel: Perfect! Take your time exploring the Palace! 🏰
Pixel: The interface has lots of cool features to discover.
Pixel: Would you like me to give you a quick tour, or do you prefer exploring on your own?
-> Give me the tour! 🎯
    <<jump InterfaceTour>>
-> I'll explore myself 🔍
    <<jump SelfExploration>>
===

title: SelfExploration
---
<<set $mood to "available">>
Pixel: Go ahead and explore! I'll be right here if you need anything!
Pixel: Just click my icon or say "Hey Pixel" when you want to chat! 💜
<<set $onboardingComplete to true>>
<<saveProfile()>>
<<minimizePixel()>>
===